# Text Input

A single line input element
 
## Samples

### Initial Text

~~~ { .haskell }
t <- textInput $ def & textInputConfig_initialValue .~ "input"
~~~

### Input Hint (aka Placeholder)

~~~ { .haskell }
t <- textInput $ 
        def & attributes .~ constDyn("placeholder" =: "type something")
~~~

### Maximal Length

~~~ { .haskell }
t <- textInput $ 
        def & attributes .~ constDyn("maxlength" =: "14")
~~~

